name: The TV Man
description: People who hate TV always seem to talk about it a lot more than people who like it. I think they just hate the fact that they love it deep down and would have no personality if it wasnt formed through strategic advertising and some comedy character catchphrase. I guess this is a sign of the corporate animal watching us. But deep down its just because I love TV of course.
